name: Travel Dress Up Games
description:
Dress up 4 different dolls with HIGE amount of fashion clothes for FREE!!!!

Amazing dress up game for travel lovers! Dress up 4 different dolls with huge amount of fashion clothes for free. Mexico , Miami and NY waiting for them!
Sevelina's Travel Plan: Mexico - Miami - NY - Paris. Sevelina's trip is go on.
She is in Mexico, colourful dresses and aztec prints are awesome and so trendy. Not so far Miami is waiting for her. Feeling the Miami heat in this dress up game! The blue sky, beaches with palm trees and tropical plants, put on some sunny clothes make her look like really hot Miami girl! Traveling means to move, and she is in NewYork now, where the fashion is probably the best developed place to visit in USA, while it definitely will not be boring to hangout around NY city. Don't forget to get I LOVE NY t-shirt!
